{"word":"G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos' - Straight","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀρθός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>orthós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>or-thos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Straight"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நிமிர்ந்த, செவ்வையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"straight, erect"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the base of <a href=\"#/G3735 - ὄρος - óros - or'-os/3735\">G3735</a>; <i>right</i> (as <i>rising</i>), that is, (perpendicularly) <i>erect</i> (figuratively <i>honest</i>), or (horizontally) <i>level</i> or <i>direct:</i> - straight, upright."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1357 - διόρθωσις - diórthōsis - dee-or'-tho-sis/1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882 - ἐπανόρθωσις - epanórthōsis - ep-an-or'-tho-sis/1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716 - ὀρθοποδέω - orthopodéō - or-thop-od-eh'-o/3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718 - ὀρθοτομέω - orthotoméō - or-thot-om-eh'-o/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719 - ὀρθρίζω - orthrízō - or-thrid'-zo/3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720 - ὀρθρινός - orthrinós - or-thrin-os'/3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721 - ὄρθριος - órthrios - or'-three-os/3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722 - ὄρθρος - órthros - or'-thros/3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723 - ὀρθῶς - orthōs - or-thoce'/3723\">G3723</a>"}]}